snippet.title: Introducing Animal Crossing: New Horizons - Happy Home Paradise
snippet.description:
Create dream vacation homes in Animal Crossing: New Horizons - Happy Home Paradise! This paid DLC for #AnimalCrossing: New Horizons arrives on 11/5 as paid DLC for $24.99, with preorders starting 10/29. 

Learn more: https://www.animal-crossing.com/new-horizons/happy-home-paradise/
